description: Claire Dames has huge boobs. Look at them. They are the size of cantaloupes. They are screaming out to be trapped, bound and punished. And their screams are heard by Cyd Black and Claire Adams, who steps in to assist Cyd in double teaming the massive sweater puppies and the woman they are attached to.
title: Adventures with Claire Dames' Huge Funbags: Part 1
